/*EXI *  TEXT('Midas DE Projected extract ctlr for loans/deposits')   *
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  Midas - Data Export module                                   *
      *                                                               *
      *  DEPXCLDNI - Projected Extract Controller for Money Market    *
      *              Loans, Deposits and Negotiable Assets Issued     *
      *                                                               *
      *  Function:  This module processes all MM Loans, Deposits and  *
      *             NA's issued and calls the module DEPXTLDNI to     *
      *             write records to the projected extract files.     *
      *                                                               *
      *  (c) Misys International Banking Systems Ltd. 2001            *
      *                                                               *
      *  Last Amend No. CDL099             Date 06Oct17               *
