      *                 CER048             Date 19May08               *
      *                 CER020             Date 19May08               *
      * Bank Fusion Midas 1.4 Base -----------------------------------*
      * Midas Plus 1.4 Base 04 ---------------------------------------*
      * Midas Plus 1.4 Base ------------------------------------------*
      * Midas Plus 1.3 ----------- Base ------------------------------*
      *                 CDL049             Date 05Jul06               *
      *                 CSD027             Date 09Dec05               *
      *                 CDL028             Date 07Feb05               *
      *                 CGL014             Date 20Oct03               *
      *                 CDL020             Date 03Feb04               *
      *                 CDL019             Date 03Feb04               *
      *                 CDL018             Date 03Feb04               *
      *                 CDL017             Date 03Feb04               *
      *                 CDL016             Date 03Feb04               *
